{"tid":1901254,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"請少少量part time","createTime":"2020-02-27T17:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T07:35:36.000Z","uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bf8e23632c78de50b6d74ceb67946f5753057a","tid":1901254,"uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"基本資料<br />\n職位 客戶服務助理<br />\n地點 九龍柯士甸附近<br />\n時薪 65 - 75起<br />\n工時 返shift 每更9個鐘 (包1個鐘飯鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n工作要求<br />\n男女皆可 兩文書寫通順 三語對答流利<br />\n有客戶服務工作經驗 (未有相關經驗但好有興趣都可以試一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n最緊要有責任心 待人友善<br />\n需要藍證保安牌<br />\n<br />\n注意事項<br />\n需要send email提交CV及進行面試<br />\n需要户外工作 (唔適合怕熱怕曬黑既同學仔 夏天真心會好熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n需要每個月報更最少四日平日 四日假日 (有考試同要交project之類既學業原因 可以特別處理)<br />\n<br />\n條team唔算好大 計過人頭只可以額外請多大概4位手足<br />\n截至日期預計3月6號下星期五 如果太多人apply會早少少截至 唔想浪費大家心機同時間 請各位見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n面試日期預計3月9號開始<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既可以tg我@smallpotatoo"},{"pid":"9a7a60c7a9b01215e0bb600724064fb994fb110d","tid":1901254,"uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:53:45.000Z","msg":"補充一下<br />\n<br />\n如果你未有藍證保安牌 但真係有興趣的話都可以send cv去安排面試睇下最後會唔會成功取錄你 我地大部份part time都係confirm offer之後去報讀<br />\n<br />\n不過drawback係幾時可以開始返工要subject to你幾時攞到藍證保安牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9878717896f89d5376e95ebf46852fc62ac43c2","tid":1901254,"uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"每日一推"},{"pid":"430cae34abe8fdb5ab981b2b0dca80e3cd2d2f75","tid":1901254,"uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"每日一推"},{"pid":"e8b6589610d7bcf9cc77a40b84fc5b408c6ac40a","tid":1901254,"uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T14:54:16.000Z","msg":"每日一推"},{"pid":"271ef92b98bafc496b84642e934b8737685eca9a","tid":1901254,"uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"每日一推"},{"pid":"e6ff34a90c1d4854d40b499e4cc9ed4429ed60e8","tid":1901254,"uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"每日一推"},{"pid":"077e070921e27e53043a49ed212b538b53a0ded8","tid":1901254,"uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:12:26.000Z","msg":"每日一推"},{"pid":"42f659f949b012e7de01222502677b6413b2adda","tid":1901254,"uid":288907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"最後一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}